channel.title: I cant log on other peoples servers
channel.description: OK so i basically gave up on making my own cause too much problems,so i tried to log on someone else server (deathscape to be exact) and when i click run the little black command prompt thingy that appears when you click run appears and disappears within a quarter of a second. what could be the problem? I'm guessing me not logging to other people's servers and not on my own is being caused by the same problem. what could be wrong?
